{"reponsecode": 0, "reponsemessage": "", "data": {"exhibit_id": "ahbwysjy_museum_xgdx_king_01", "exhibition_name": "安徽文明史陈列（一）", "location": "32,0", "name": "河南汝窑", "size": "", "like": 0, "share_url": "mob/exhibit/detail?exhibit_id=3444", "is_favorited": 0, "_3d_url": "", "description": "汝窑，因产于汝州而得名，窑址在今河南省宝丰县大营镇清凉寺村。汝瓷位居宋代“汝、官、哥、钧、定”五大名窑之首。相传，宋徽宗曾经做过一个梦，梦到大雨过后，远处天空有一抹神秘的天青色，格外令人着迷。醒来之后，他便写下一句诗：“雨过天青云破处”，拿给工匠参考，让他们烧制出这种颜色。一时间，不知难倒了多少工匠，最后汝州工匠技高一筹，烧出了令宋徽宗满意的天青色，而天青色釉也就成为汝窑瓷器的典型特征。", "images": ["content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/1jpVbkDoj_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/1jpVbkDoj1_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/1jpVbkDoj2_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/1jpVbkDoj3_s.webp", "content/fileroot/museum/ahbwysjy_museum/image/1jpVbkDoj4_s.webp"], "audio": [], "video": {"videourl": "", "img": ""}, "ispaid": 1}}